'''埃德娜·克拉巴佩尔'''（{{lang-en|'''Edna Krabappel'''}}）是动画片《[[辛普森一家|辛普森一家]]》中的角色，由[[瑪西婭·華萊士|瑪西婭·華萊士]]配音，并在剧集“{{tsl|en|Bart the Genius|Bart the Genius}}”中首次出现。她是[[巴特·辛普森|巴特·辛普森]][[春田镇小學|春田镇小學]][[四年級|四年級]][[教師|教師]]和[[内德·弗兰德|内德·弗兰德]]的現任妻子。 克拉巴佩尔是華萊士唯一配音角色。華萊士逝世於2013年10月，節目的製片人宣布，他們打算引退。<ref name="WallaceDeathEW">{{cite web|url=http://insidetv.ew.com/2013/10/26/marcia-wallace-actress-from-the-simpsons-and-the-bob-newhart-show-dies-at-70/|title=Marcia Wallace, actress from 'The Simpsons' and 'The Bob Newhart Show', dies at 70|publisher=Entertainment Weekly|date=October 26, 2013|accessdate=October 26, 2013|archive-date=2015-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150115051038/http://insidetv.ew.com/2013/10/26/marcia-wallace-actress-from-the-simpsons-and-the-bob-newhart-show-dies-at-70/|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="bbcwallace">{{cite web | url= http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-24802207 | title= The Simpsons pays tribute to late actress Marcia Wallace | date= November 4, 2013 | publisher= [[BBC_News|BBC News]] | quote= Sunday's edition of ''The Simpsons'' was preceded on the Fox channel in the US by a re-run of 2011 episode [[The_Ned-liest_Catch|The Ned-liest Catch]]. Wallace appeared in 178 episodes in all, voicing grumpy fourth-grade teacher Edna in all but three of them. The actress's death was confirmed on 26 October by ''The Simpsons''{{'}} executive producer [[Al_Jean|Al Jean]], who said she had been "brilliant and gracious." "She was beloved by all at ''The Simpsons'' and we intend to retire her irreplaceable character,' he said in a [http://www.facebook.com/TheSimpsons/posts/10151751306093697 message] on Facebook." | accessdate= November 5, 2013 | archive-date= 2015-03-04 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150304100539/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-24802207 | dead-url= no }}</ref>

